{"tid":1130402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無你想要圖]美國(賓州)食品加工廠女員工失足墮碎肉機內身亡 (21:27)","createTime":"2019-04-29T04:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T07:04:31.000Z","uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4277672516c0540dfe0113cbdc8e72d9e79676e0","tid":1130402,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"美國食品加工廠女員工失足墮碎肉機內身亡 (21:27)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190428/s00005/e944984cb31f7d6addfaa6faba86ed3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190428%2Fs00005%2Fe944984cb31f7d6addfaa6faba86ed3c.jpg&h=510d18f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n35歲的格林葛（小圖）於食品加工廠工作期間失足跌入碎肉機內死亡。（網上圖片/明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n美國賓夕法尼亞州一名在食品加工廠工作的女子，工作期間失足跌入碎肉機內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n35歲女子格林葛（Jill Greninger）上周二（23日）如常站在梯子上，在大型碎肉機旁工作，其間失足跌入碎肉機內，其他同事聽到碎肉機發出異常聲響始驚悉事件。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員接報趕到現場，花兩個多小時拆開涉事碎肉機，抬出格林葛的屍體，職業安全與健康管理局正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n（全國廣播公司）"},{"pid":"296f6dd6b76df5d53247028ae562fa9652400cc1","tid":1130402,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"咁都搵到佢既屍體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0378052e64d66e50c118446f564520562d9a6e96","tid":1130402,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:28:23.000Z","msg":"個死法好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"f0b83874a2c50f0d2b430bf3c64908400996599e","tid":1130402,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"好撚痛，佢死個一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb065b0441c9f71a63213796e32735d61d90b57c","tid":1130402,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:20:58.00